title: Cisco Catalyst 9000: StackWise Virtual Switch Redundancy State
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/network/cisco
license: GPL
distribution: kuhn-ruess
description:
 Monitors the StackWise Virtual (VSS) member switches of a Cisco Catalyst
 9000 series switch. Role and state of each member switch are read from the
 CISCO-STACKWISE-MIB (cswSwitchRole, cswSwitchState).

 The switch state is OK when it is "ready" and CRITICAL otherwise. The
 switch role is OK unless an expected role is configured and the actual role
 differs, in which case the check becomes CRITICAL.

 The expected switch role can be configured via the rule
 "Cisco Catalyst 9k redundancy State".

item:
 The current switch number.

inventory:
 One service is created per member switch. The discovered role is stored as
 the default expected role.
